summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the general municipal election of November 4, 1969 and submitting thereat the proposed Charter Amendments contemplated by Resolutions 22144, 22145, 22147, 22148, 22149, 22150, 22151, and 22152; and requiring the City Clerk to certify to the Director of Department of Records and Elections of King County as required by law, said proposed amendments in the form of specified ballot titles and said amendments in full, and providing for publication thereof.
